videos.description: Oregon's Dillon Brooks gets ejected for kicking Washington State's Josh Hawkinson in the groin in the first half of the No. 15 Ducks' 85-66 win over Washington State.
videos.headline: Brooks ejected as Oregon cruises past Washington State
